      USDA, Agricultural Research Service, National Center for Genetic
      Resources Preservation is committed to making its web sites accessible
      to all USDA customers and employees.  All of the agency web sites are
      undergoing review and redesign as necessary to ensure that they meet or
      exceed the requirements of Section 508 of the Rehabilitation Act of
      1973.

      Many of our web sites currently meet the Section 508 accessibility
      standards.  Furthermore, USDA-ARS, National Center for Genetic
      Resources Preservation continues to work on making all web sites
      accessible.  Thank you very much for your patience through this
      redesign process.  If you have any comments or suggestions for
      improvement, please contact the Web Master of this page.

